es to mutate and alter those living and dead, Hiromi and Yabu attempt to get free from a zombie swarm and find help for Hideo. Across Japan, those who are fully ZQN begin to band together in surprising ways.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-04","rating":4.5,"review":"","added":9999944,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989647","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 15","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828279/140/5b87/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_15.jpg","isbn":"978-4091862846","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2014","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"As the ZQN virus continues to mutate and alter those living and dead, Hiromi and Yabu attempt to get free from a zombie swarm and find help for Hideo. Across Japan, those who are fully ZQN begin to band together in surprising ways.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-04","rating":4.5,"review":"","added":9999943,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989646","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 14","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828278/140/94ab/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_14.jpg","isbn":"978-4091858771","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2014","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Near Tokyo, Hideo and the other survivors find camaraderie and even moments of romance as they slowly make their way back into the city. New horrors are encountered and new weapons are found, as old fears continue to haunt expressive, traumatized Hideo.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-04","rating":4.5,"review":"","added":9999942,"hdCover":""}]');

INSERT OR IGNORE INTO library_items (
  id,title,author,item_type,reading_status,cover_url,hd_cover_url,isbn,publisher,
  publication_date,language,series,genres,annotation,read_date,rating,review,quotes,
  acquired_on,purchase_cost_cents,is_sold,sold_on,sale_price_cents,added
)
SELECT
  json_extract(value,'$.id'),json_extract(value,'$.title'),json_extract(value,'$.author'),
  json_extract(value,'$.type'),json_extract(value,'$.status'),json_extract(value,'$.cover'),
  json_extract(value,'$.hdCover'),json_extract(value,'$.isbn'),json_extract(value,'$.publisher'),
  json_extract(value,'$.pubDate'),json_extract(value,'$.language'),json_extract(value,'$.series'),
  json_extract(value,'$.genres'),json_extract(value,'$.annotation'),json_extract(value,'$.read'),
  json_extract(value,'$.rating'),json_extract(value,'$.review'),json_extract(value,'$.quotes'),
  json_extract(value,'$.acquired'),CASE WHEN json_extract(value,'$.cost') IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE round(json_extract(value,'$.cost')*100) END,
  CASE WHEN json_extract(value,'$.sold') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END,json_extract(value,'$.soldDate'),
  CASE WHEN json_extract(value,'$.soldPrice') IS NULL THEN NULL ELSE round(json_extract(value,'$.soldPrice')*100) END,
  json_extract(value,'$.added')
FROM json_each('[{"id":"0989645","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 13","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828276/140/64f7/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_13.jpg","isbn":"978-4091855749","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2013","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Near Tokyo, Hideo and the other survivors find camaraderie and even moments of romance as they slowly make their way back into the city. New horrors are encountered and new weapons are found, as old fears continue to haunt expressive, traumatized Hideo.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-04","rating":4.5,"review":"","added":9999941,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989644","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 12","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828275/140/0afc/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_12.jpg","isbn":"978-4091852403","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2013","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"A global zombie outbreak threatens to wipe out civilization! In Japan, some of the infected have been able to hold onto their humanity while exhibiting superhuman ZQN powers. As Hiromi evolves, affected by a zombie baby''s bite, will Hideo also exhibit powers linked to the bite on his hand? Other afflicted humans seem to have supernatural abilities, too, like the leader of the Cult of Kurusu.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4.5,"review":"","added":9999940,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989643","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 11","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828270/140/4167/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_11.jpg","isbn":"978-4091848802","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2013","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"A global zombie outbreak threatens to wipe out civilization! In Japan, some of the infected have been able to hold onto their humanity while exhibiting superhuman ZQN powers. As Hiromi evolves, affected by a zombie baby''s bite, will Hideo also exhibit powers linked to the bite on his hand? Other afflicted humans seem to have supernatural abilities, too, like the leader of the Cult of Kurusu.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999939,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989642","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 10","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828269/140/4474/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_10.jpg","isbn":"978-4091847294","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2012","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Our three key survivors must help each other heal up mentally and physically, as Hiromi''s mysterious affliction continues to evolve. Hideo and Yabu grow closer as the mysterious Cult of Kurusu spreads across the country.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999938,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989641","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 9","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828268/140/6fe6/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_9.jpg","isbn":"I am a Hero,  Volume","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2012","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Our three key survivors must help each other heal up mentally and physically, as Hiromi''s mysterious affliction continues to evolve. Hideo and Yabu grow closer as the mysterious Cult of Kurusu spreads across the country.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999937,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989640","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 8","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828266/140/8ed2/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_8.jpg","isbn":"978-4091842466","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2012","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"After teaming up with a larger group of survivors living above an outlet mall, Hideo, Hiromi, and Mr. Araki are betrayed. Now subservient to a band of strange men with odd post-apocalyptic rules, will Hideo find a way to rescue the sick, partially mutated Hiromi? If they can escape with a few new allies and leave the core, rotten group of survivors behind, maybe they have a chance in this deadly new world.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999936,"hdCover":""},{"id":"098963f","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 7","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828265/140/61d8/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_7.jpg","isbn":"978-4091840509","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2011","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"After teaming up with a larger group of survivors living above an outlet mall, Hideo, Hiromi, and Mr. Araki are betrayed. Now subservient to a band of strange men with odd post-apocalyptic rules, will Hideo find a way to rescue the sick, partially mutated Hiromi? If they can escape with a few new allies and leave the core, rotten group of survivors behind, maybe they have a chance in this deadly new world.","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999935,"hdCover":""},{"id":"098963e","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 6","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828262/140/8042/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_6.jpg","isbn":"978-4091838278","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2011","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Hideo and his new ward, young Hiromi, head out of the desolate forest they''ve been hiding in, hoping to find refuge at a local shrine. Once there, however, they soon realize that populated areas are just as dangerous as the haunted woods they''ve left! A new ally may help them find a safe place to hole up again - but one quick, deadly bite could threaten all of their lives!","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999934,"hdCover":""},{"id":"098963d","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 5","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828258/140/cb03/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_5.jpg","isbn":"978-4091835345","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2010","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Hideo and his new ward, young Hiromi, head out of the desolate forest they''ve been hiding in, hoping to find refuge at a local shrine. Once there, however, they soon realize that populated areas are just as dangerous as the haunted woods they''ve left! A new ally may help them find a safe place to hole up again - but one quick, deadly bite could threaten all of their lives!","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999933,"hdCover":""},{"id":"098963c","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 4","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828256/140/7d85/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_4.jpg","isbn":"978-4091833778","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2010","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Having escaped being eaten by his zombie girlfriend and torn apart by his infected co-workers, Hideo Suzuki continues to head away from civilization and the bloodthirsty hordes taking over Japan. In a \"suicide forest\" that winds up being just as dangerous as the city, Hideo finds a young girl who needs help and who could also help him more than he realizes! The zombie apocalypse has never been more surreal!","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999932,"hdCover":""},{"id":"098963b","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 3","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828184/140/a929/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_3.jpg","isbn":"978-4091831576","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2010","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"Having escaped being eaten by his zombie girlfriend and torn apart by his infected co-workers, Hideo Suzuki continues to head away from civilization and the bloodthirsty hordes taking over Japan. In a \"suicide forest\" that winds up being just as dangerous as the city, Hideo finds a young girl who needs help and who could also help him more than he realizes! The zombie apocalypse has never been more surreal!","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999931,"hdCover":""},{"id":"098963a","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 2","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828167/140/193a/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_2.jpg","isbn":"978-4091827791","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2009","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"A mentally unhinged manga artist witnesses the beginning of a zombie outbreak in Tokyo, and he’s certain of only two things: he’s destined to be the city’s hero, and he possesses something quite rare in Japan-an actual firearm!","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999930,"hdCover":""},{"id":"0989639","title":"I am a Hero, Volume 1","author":"Kengo Hanazawa","type":"Книга","cover":"https://s1.livelib.ru/boocover/1002828135/140/00bb/Kengo_Hanazawa__I_am_a_Hero_Volume_1.jpg","isbn":"978-4091825803","publisher":"Shogakukan","pubDate":"2009","language":"Японский","series":"I am a Hero","genres":[],"annotation":"A mentally unhinged manga artist witnesses the beginning of a zombie outbreak in Tokyo, and he’s certain of only two things: he’s destined to be the city’s hero, and he possesses something quite rare in Japan-an actual firearm!","acquired":"","cost":null,"sold":false,"soldDate":"","soldPrice":null,"quotes":[],"status":"Прочитал","read":"2023-03","rating":4,"review":"","added":9999929,"hdCover":""}]');

